 and 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

passionate
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 on one axis and by 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

attachment
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

discernment
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 on the other.
 The people in the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

passionate discernment
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 quadrant are special.
 They are passionate about what they do but also have “discernment”, the
 ability to see things without context, without personal attachment.
 It's rare to find managers in this quadrant.
 It requires a deep connection and commitment to an organization's mission
 and a knack to see without judging.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
These people are your playmakers, your change agents, and the most impactful
 leaders in your org.
 Find them.
 Learn from them.
 Be like them.
\end_layout

